comment.author: 95731483@N02
comment._content:
The squadron is misidentified.
An F-6C (see the camera port just in front of the tail wheel) the large "5" of the tail number indicates that this airplane is from the 118th TRS 23rd FG. Their tail numbers were from 550 - 600 until 1945 when they changed to 150 - 199.
